These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
House: futuristic, victorian, cape-cod, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, frog, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, zinnia, sunflower
1. the colombian is the owner of the snake##1
2. the indonesian is between the cape-cod house and the townhouse house##2
3. the colombian is the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who growszinnia is the cape-cod house##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the townhouse house##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the victorian house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House   | victorian | townhouse   | futuristic  | cape-cod  |
| Pet   | rat    | snake    | mouse      | frog    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Flower     | sunflower  | aconite       | dahlia    | zinnia     |

