.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, modern, palace
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, july, september
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, quad-bike, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the roller##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the owner of the frog and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person driving the van is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the modern house##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House         | palace | art-deco    | modern  | farmhouse    |
| Birthday   | november      | january  | september  | july |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Transport         | roller    | van | quad-bike | subway |

