.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea, mirinda
House: farmhouse, tower, cape-cod, craftsman
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, classical, funk, house
1. the paramedic is the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the lawyer is the craftsman house##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is between the farmhouse house and the craftsman house##2
9. the cape-cod house is between the person drinking iced-tea and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage        | soy-milk | iced-tea     | almond-milk   | mirinda     |
| House       | tower   | farmhouse   | cape-cod | craftsman |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | classical | metal  | house    |

