.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, hiking, puzzles, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, tiparillo, blend, chaman
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, tulip, iris
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 4. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who growslily##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Hobby           | camping  | woodworking | hiking     | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Cigar           | tiparillo       | chaman    | blend      | old-henry           |
| Flower         | rose | lily   | iris   | tulip         |

