.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, guinea-pig, goat
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, spanish, japanese, indian
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, gardening, magic-tricks
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the indian is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the indian##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the lawyer is the spanish##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the russian##2
10. the japanese is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | frog         | guinea-pig         | turtle     | goat      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Nationality   | russian      | japanese       | indian    | spanish       |
| Hobby         | card-games     | gardening       | magic-tricks | collecting |

