There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, bellflower, tulip
1. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who growstulip and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person eating kale is between the person who's birthday is in january and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who growsdahlia and the dutch##2
4. the person eating potato is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food           | potato | kale | pepper  | artichoke |
| Birthday   | october      | may       | january     | november      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Flower         | bellflower   | tulip    | begonia | dahlia   |

