 7. the colombian is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the spanish is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes white##2
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the italian##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
